    "body" : "<p>Try:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Iterator&lt;Map.Entry&lt;String,String&gt;&gt; iter = testMap.entrySet().iterator();\nwhile (iter.hasNext()) {\n    Map.Entry&lt;String,String&gt; entry = iter.next();\n    if(\"Sample\".equalsIgnoreCase(entry.getValue())){\n        iter.remove();\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>With Java 1.8 and onwards you can do the above in just one line:</p>\n\n<pre><code>testMap.entrySet().removeIf(entry -&gt; \"Sample\".equalsIgnoreCase(entry.getValue()));\n</code></pre>\n"
